percentFemale: Most of the direct and indirect beneficiaries are women. As for example, 72% of people staying or working at the Placement Centre from Sculeni, Ungheni are women, and 38% - men. As for the Singerei Hospital, 64% of workers and patients are women and 36% are men. In the Chisinau multi-story building beneficiary of a photovoltaic system, 65% of the residents are women and 35% are men.
